    "name": "task",
    "purpose": "Owns agent task runtime. Task drives the per-task worker thread: it sends the initial status, triggers the initial plan through Step, routes task and step events, forwards execution events to execution_hub.route_event, and routes plan events to plan_hub.route_event. TaskState holds the session context, task signature, user request, model backend, session event sender, PlanHub, ExecutionHub, and a StepId-keyed step WorkQueue, plus a manual Debug impl.",
